{
  "video_id": "YvFCZ5tFk5Q",
  "title": "Financial Statements - Lecture 3 - Business Activities",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 10090.0,
      "end_time": 10750.0,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10750.0,
      "end_time": 11770.0,
      "text": "Else here."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11770.0,
      "end_time": 13390.0,
      "text": "In this video, we&#39;ll be exploring"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13390.0,
      "end_time": 15380.0,
      "text": "the classification of business activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15380.0,
      "end_time": 17540.0,
      "text": "and why this information is important."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17540.0,
      "end_time": 19480.0,
      "text": "There are three main business activities--"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19480.0,
      "end_time": 21752.0,
      "text": "financing, investing, and operating."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21752.0,
      "end_time": 23710.0,
      "text": "In order to better understand these activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23710.0,
      "end_time": 26089.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s start a business and walk through them."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26089.0,
      "end_time": 27880.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say you want to start a business that"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27880.0,
      "end_time": 29255.0,
      "text": "develops iPhone apps."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29255.0,
      "end_time": 30880.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve seen other people do it, and you"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 30880.0,
      "end_time": 34330.0,
      "text": "figure it&#39;s an excellent way to join the 250,000 people who"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 34330.0,
      "end_time": 36880.0,
      "text": "start businesses every year in Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 36880.0,
      "end_time": 38590.0,
      "text": "If you start this business, what do you"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38590.0,
      "end_time": 40450.0,
      "text": "think you&#39;ll have to do first?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40450.0,
      "end_time": 43300.0,
      "text": "The first thing is to get financing for your business."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43300.0,
      "end_time": 47320.0,
      "text": "Financing activities are all about getting or repaying cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 47320.0,
      "end_time": 49030.0,
      "text": "You may have savings of your own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 49030.0,
      "end_time": 50620.0,
      "text": "but you might need to borrow money."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 50620.0,
      "end_time": 52480.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s called debt financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 52480.0,
      "end_time": 55000.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a corporation, you can sell shares."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 55000.0,
      "end_time": 56710.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s called equity financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 56710.0,
      "end_time": 60230.0,
      "text": "Financing activities are all about funding your business."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 60230.0,
      "end_time": 62380.0,
      "text": "Remember that involves not just getting the funds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 62380.0,
      "end_time": 65620.0,
      "text": "but also paying them back or paying dividends."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 65620.0,
      "end_time": 69010.0,
      "text": "After you raise the funds, you&#39;ll need to spend it."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 69010.0,
      "end_time": 70780.0,
      "text": "Investing activities is when you buy"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 70780.0,
      "end_time": 73570.0,
      "text": "the things you need in order to run your business, generally"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 73570.0,
      "end_time": 75490.0,
      "text": "property, plant, and equipment."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 75490.0,
      "end_time": 78010.0,
      "text": "For instance, for your app development company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 78010.0,
      "end_time": 79930.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll have to buy computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 79930.0,
      "end_time": 83560.0,
      "text": "Any long-lived assets that you use to operate a business"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 83560.0,
      "end_time": 85610.0,
      "text": "are considered investing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 85610.0,
      "end_time": 88270.0,
      "text": "Investing activities generally involve the use of cash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 88270.0,
      "end_time": 89890.0,
      "text": "because you tend to spend, spend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 89890.0,
      "end_time": 93190.0,
      "text": "spend to get what you need for your business to operate."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 93190.0,
      "end_time": 94960.0,
      "text": "Once you&#39;ve financed your business"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 94960.0,
      "end_time": 96520.0,
      "text": "and bought what you need to run it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 96520.0,
      "end_time": 99310.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to have to begin operating the business."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 99310.0,
      "end_time": 100810.0,
      "text": "That would include selling your apps"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 100810.0,
      "end_time": 103660.0,
      "text": "to earn revenue, service revenue, in this case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 103660.0,
      "end_time": 106210.0,
      "text": "and all the costs you&#39;ll incur to earn that revenue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 106210.0,
      "end_time": 108520.0,
      "text": "things like paying the salaries of your employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 108520.0,
      "end_time": 111280.0,
      "text": "the rent for your space, and anything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 111280.0,
      "end_time": 113560.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re using, consuming, or incurring costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 113560.0,
      "end_time": 115330.0,
      "text": "to help you generate revenue, those"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 115330.0,
      "end_time": 117070.0,
      "text": "are considered operating expenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 117070.0,
      "end_time": 118960.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re part of the operating activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 118960.0,
      "end_time": 120089.0,
      "text": "of a business."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 120089.0,
      "end_time": 121630.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s double check your understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 121630.0,
      "end_time": 123530.0,
      "text": "of the types of business activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 123530.0,
      "end_time": 126850.0,
      "text": "Remember to pause the video and answer first."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 126850.0,
      "end_time": 130360.0,
      "text": "In your app development company, if you sold your old equipment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 130360.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131560.0,
      "text": "it would be considered an--"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 137130.0,
      "end_time": 139980.0,
      "text": "if you said A, operating activities, because you sold"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 139980.0,
      "end_time": 142200.0,
      "text": "something, you&#39;re incorrect."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 142200.0,
      "end_time": 144270.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t sell old equipment day to day"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 144270.0,
      "end_time": 145840.0,
      "text": "as part of your operations."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 145840.0,
      "end_time": 147990.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s not operating activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 147990.0,
      "end_time": 151530.0,
      "text": "If you said C, financing, because it brought in cash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 151530.0,
      "end_time": 153120.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re wrong also."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 153120.0,
      "end_time": 156480.0,
      "text": "Financing involves only debt or equity financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 156480.0,
      "end_time": 159480.0,
      "text": "The correct answer is B, investing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 159480.0,
      "end_time": 162570.0,
      "text": "Note that in each activity, what goes into that activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 162570.0,
      "end_time": 164710.0,
      "text": "comes out of that same activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 164710.0,
      "end_time": 167100.0,
      "text": "The purchase of equipment is recorded under investing."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 167100.0,
      "end_time": 170010.0,
      "text": "And, therefore, the sale of equipment is also investing."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 170010.0,
      "end_time": 172110.0,
      "text": "Similarly, if a company borrows money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 172110.0,
      "end_time": 174150.0,
      "text": "it would be under financing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 174150.0,
      "end_time": 176040.0,
      "text": "When they pay the money back, that would also"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 176040.0,
      "end_time": 177840.0,
      "text": "go under financing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 177840.0,
      "end_time": 183180.0,
      "text": "What it comes in, it comes out of, the exact same activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 183180.0,
      "end_time": 184800.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s practice a bit more and look"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 184800.0,
      "end_time": 186810.0,
      "text": "at a few other transactions."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 186810.0,
      "end_time": 190020.0,
      "text": "For the next four slides, classify each transaction"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 190020.0,
      "end_time": 192787.0,
      "text": "as operating, investing, or financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 192787.0,
      "end_time": 194370.0,
      "text": "You should also be able to say if it&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 194370.0,
      "end_time": 196230.0,
      "text": "an inflow or an outflow."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 196230.0,
      "end_time": 199440.0,
      "text": "Remember, to do this, you have to know the definition"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 199440.0,
      "end_time": 200760.0,
      "text": "of each of the activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 200760.0,
      "end_time": 204210.0,
      "text": "If you don&#39;t, your answers will not only be wrong here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 204210.0,
      "end_time": 206700.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;ll also be wrong on a test or exam when"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 206700.0,
      "end_time": 208430.0,
      "text": "you eventually write it."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 208430.0,
      "end_time": 211952.0,
      "text": "Dividends of a 100,000 are paid to shareholders."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 215120.0,
      "end_time": 218690.0,
      "text": "Dividends involve shareholders, and the sale or repurchase"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 218690.0,
      "end_time": 221030.0,
      "text": "of shares is a financing activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 221030.0,
      "end_time": 223520.0,
      "text": "and, therefore, so are the dividends payment."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223520.0,
      "end_time": 227890.0,
      "text": "Financing activity, outflow."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 227890.0,
      "end_time": 231850.0,
      "text": "Payment of 250,000 are collected from customers."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 238000.0,
      "text": "Anything having to do with customers"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 238000.0,
      "end_time": 241130.0,
      "text": "is part of the day-to-day operations of the business."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 241130.0,
      "end_time": 246240.0,
      "text": "So the correct answer is operating activities, inflow."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 246240.0,
      "end_time": 252490.0,
      "text": "Pay $20,000 to renovate a store."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 252490.0,
      "end_time": 255400.0,
      "text": "This is an investment in future revenue generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 255400.0,
      "end_time": 259769.0,
      "text": "and, therefore, is part of investing activities, outflow."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 259769.0,
      "end_time": 261459.0,
      "text": "Last one."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 261459.0,
      "end_time": 263550.0,
      "text": "Interest is paid on an outstanding loan."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 267780.0,
      "end_time": 272010.0,
      "text": "Now, the answer to this one is either operating or financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 272010.0,
      "end_time": 274860.0,
      "text": "IFRS says that interest paid on a loan"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 274860.0,
      "end_time": 276780.0,
      "text": "may go into financing activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 276780.0,
      "end_time": 279570.0,
      "text": "because the taking of a loan and repaying of a loan"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279570.0,
      "end_time": 281470.0,
      "text": "is part of financing activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 281470.0,
      "end_time": 283920.0,
      "text": "So the interest payments can be also."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 283920.0,
      "end_time": 286380.0,
      "text": "But IFRS also says that interest costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 286380.0,
      "end_time": 288330.0,
      "text": "are an expense on the income statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 288330.0,
      "end_time": 290490.0,
      "text": "and are paid to support the day-to-day activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 290490.0,
      "end_time": 291540.0,
      "text": "of the business."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291540.0,
      "end_time": 294300.0,
      "text": "Therefore, they can be included instead as part"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294300.0,
      "end_time": 296121.0,
      "text": "of operating activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296121.0,
      "end_time": 299070.0,
      "text": "Under IFRS, the choice is the company&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299070.0,
      "end_time": 302250.0,
      "text": "However, once the company makes a choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 302250.0,
      "end_time": 305400.0,
      "text": "they must continue placing it in the same activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 305400.0,
      "end_time": 306960.0,
      "text": "into the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 306960.0,
      "end_time": 309420.0,
      "text": "Note that ASPE only allows interest payments"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 309420.0,
      "end_time": 312750.0,
      "text": "to be included as part of operating activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 312750.0,
      "end_time": 315600.0,
      "text": "Why is knowing about the different activities important?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315600.0,
      "end_time": 317310.0,
      "text": "Accounting is an information system"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317310.0,
      "end_time": 319470.0,
      "text": "that provides financial information for decision"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 319470.0,
      "end_time": 320400.0,
      "text": "makers."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 320400.0,
      "end_time": 323100.0,
      "text": "That information is useful only if those using it"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 323100.0,
      "end_time": 324570.0,
      "text": "can understand it."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 324570.0,
      "end_time": 326970.0,
      "text": "Remember that the main users of financial information"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 326970.0,
      "end_time": 329340.0,
      "text": "are investors, lenders, and creditors."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 329340.0,
      "end_time": 332670.0,
      "text": "Many of those users believe that the statement of cash flow"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 332670.0,
      "end_time": 334950.0,
      "text": "is useful for predicting how much cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 334950.0,
      "end_time": 337680.0,
      "text": "will be available in the future for either repaying"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 337680.0,
      "end_time": 339840.0,
      "text": "debts or paying dividends."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 339840.0,
      "end_time": 342750.0,
      "text": "The statement of cash flow is divided into three activities--"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 342750.0,
      "end_time": 345065.0,
      "text": "financing, investing, and operating."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 345065.0,
      "end_time": 347190.0,
      "text": "By understanding the different types of activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 347190.0,
      "end_time": 349920.0,
      "text": "you can tie that understanding into the structure of the cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 349920.0,
      "end_time": 351990.0,
      "text": "flow statement, which we&#39;ll be covering"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 351990.0,
      "end_time": 354620.0,
      "text": "in the next series of videos."
    }
  ]
}